examples.en: A new coin was issued.
Smoke issued from the chimneys.
Blood issued from the wound.
The army issued new rifles to the troops.
He was issued a citation.
examples.ru: Ему прислали / выдали повестку в суд.

examples.en: They have issued a general warning.
He just issued his first solo album.
examples.ru: Он только что выпустил свой первый сольный альбом.

examples.en: They issued a retrospective report.
The judge issued a summons.
He had not been issued with a licence.
He issued a writ against the newspaper.
examples.ru: Он выдал ордер на арест имущества газеты.

examples.en: Water issued from the hole in the wall.
examples.ru: Из отверстия в стене вытекала вода.

examples.en: Smoke issued forth at several orifices.
A severe storm warning has been issued.
The court has issued a definitive ruling.
The booklet was issued by the government.
The judge issued a reprimand from the bench.
He issued a vehement denial of the accusation.
They issued us with free passes to the theatre.
examples.ru: Они выдали нам бесплатные билеты в театр.

examples.en: The magistrate issued a warrant for his arrest.
examples.ru: Судья выдал ордер на его арест.

examples.en: The company issued warrants for 300,000 shares.
examples.ru: Компания выпустила варранты на приобретение трёхсот тысяч акций.

examples.en: The senator issued a flat denial of all charges.
The two ministers have issued a joint statement.
examples.ru: Министры двух стран выступили с совместным заявлением.

examples.en: The school issued the pupils with new textbooks.
The police have issued a warrant for her arrest.
examples.ru: Полиция выдала ордер на её арест.

examples.en: The Commission issued a directive on food prices.
examples.ru: Еврокомиссия издала директиву о ценах на продукты питания.

examples.en: The king issued a decree forbidding all protests.
examples.ru: Король издал указ, запрещающий все протесты.

examples.en: The government issued a statement about the strike.
examples.ru: Правительство выпустило сообщение по поводу этой забастовки.

examples.en: The policy document will be issued to all employees.
examples.ru: Условия договора будут выдаваться на руки всем сотрудникам.

examples.en: Each employee will be issued an identification card.
